title: Baseball Holds Tennessee Tech to Three Hits, Takes Series Opener 5-2 - Morehead State University Athletics - MSU Eagles
content: Baseball Holds Tennessee Tech to Three Hits, Takes Series Opener 5-2 - Morehead State University Athletics  MSU Eagles
description: COOKEVILLE, Tenn. â€“ After struggling on the road to begin the season, the Morehead State baseball team has won two in a row away from Allen Field after taking the series opener 5-2 over Tennessee Tech Friday. The Eagles (11-14, 3-1 OVC) used a three-run ninth, small ball and great pitching to shut down one of the best offenses in the OVC to win their fourth straight game.
